# VoiceNexus AI root environment reference.
# Each app owns its runtime variables. Copy these files before local development:
#
#   apps/api/.env.example -> apps/api/.env
#   apps/web/.env.example -> apps/web/.env.local
#
# MongoDB Atlas is the Phase 1 database. The backend service layer uses repository
# interfaces so the persistence implementation can be migrated later without
# rewriting application services.
